                           MCW / BLAST Installation

In order to "INSTALL" mcw and blast, one should only need to run:

  make install

from the root of this distribution.  This will build mcw, blastall, and all
required tools and libraries.  The compiled binaries are available in:

  target

Note that there are currently no "configure" scripts and one needs to change
several files to modify the configuration.

